== Uburezi ==
Afite impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bijyanye no guhanga no kubungabunga ibidukikije byubatswe mu 2015, <ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/magazine/following-my-passion-is-the-best-decision-i-made-3297140</ref> yakuye muri [[kaminuza y'u Rwanda]] . <ref>https://www.lionessesofafrica.com/blog/2021/5/30/kevine-kagirimpundu-a-passion-driven-producer-of-eco-footwear-in-rwanda</ref>.Akaba yarize amashuri yisumbuye muri lucee

== Umwuga ==
[https://shop.uzuriky.com/ UZURI K&Y] ni uruganda rwo mu [[Rwanda]] rufite icyicaro i [[Kigali]] mu [[Rwanda]] kandi rwanditswe muri RDB kuva muri Kamena 2013, rukora umurongo winkweto z'ufunguye. batezimbere tekinike yumwimerere yo gukora inkweto nyafurika,  imiterere idasanzwe, hamwe nuburyo bwihariye bwo gutegura ibikoresho. <ref>https://www.lionessesofafrica.com/blog/2021/5/30/kevine-kagirimpundu-a-passion-driven-producer-of-eco-footwear-in-rwanda</ref>

== Ibyo Kevine avuga nyuma yokwihangira umurimo ==
Ubu twafungutse mumitekereze dufite ibitekerezo byo gupima ibikorwa byacu. Gupima ubucuruzi bigomba gutegurwa kandi ntitwari dufite igitekerezo cyo kubikora mbere yuko twinjira muri mu mwuga <ref>https://www.ikeasocialentrepreneurship.org/en/social-entrepreneurs/uzuri-ky</ref>
